  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Tetsuwan Atom is an action platformer video-game developed by Zamuse and published by Banpresto and released for Super Famicom on 1994 in Japan.\n\nThe game is a retelling of the 1952 manga with artworks based in the 1980 series (Uran and Kid Atlas are pretty notifiable). In the story, Atom goes fighting several obstacles like evil robots and monsters.",
